  "text": "Attack trees can model the sub-goals the attacker needs to achieve so that the attack is successful [CITATION_1] . Information security has been the main application area of attack trees. Attack trees are usually analysed qualitatively, but they can also be analysed quantitatively in the manner of fault trees.",
